Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:01:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a little treat for you today.\NA friend of ours has prepared sort of a slide presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.51,0:01:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of what our life is like on the ranch.\NSo a lot of the pictures that you're going to see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,were taken of our personal life.\NAnd in the bookstore, if you purchase $100,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you get this video free.\NSo we wanted to give that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful, and I think you're really going to enjoy it\Nand get out the Kleenex.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:20:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,For all of you that aren't familiar with our work\Nand our first-time comers, this is our ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And we did a whole series on that in 2002.\NAnd this is our little ego that we carry around with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And we don't oppose it.\NWe just embrace it and love it and know that it's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is what the teddy bear represents.\NHa, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good God.\NWhere are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:21:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be somebody out there.\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sing-song kitty.\NSing-song kitty, won't you kind me, oh, keen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned this from my father 80 years ago.\NSing-song kitty, won't you kind me, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Keem, oh, kind, oh, dar, oh, ah, many, I, many, oh, many, rum,\Nstum, fum, me, diddle, soup, peck, fetty, won't you lick them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,mick them.\NSing-song kitty, won't you kind me, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NSing-song kitty, won't you kind me, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:22:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Keem, oh, kind, oh, dar, oh, ah, many, I, many, oh, many, rum,\Nstum, fum, me, diddle, soup, peck, fetty, won't you lick them,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,mick them.\NSing-song kitty, won't you kind me, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NThat's the love I got from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He was that.\NAnd then I'd say, say it slow, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,0:22:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I memorized it.\NHa, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was love 80 years ago.\NHa, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Keem, oh, kind, oh, dar, oh, ah, many, I, many, oh, many,\Nrum, stum, fum, me, diddle, soup, peck, fetty, won't you lick
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,them, mick them.\NSing-song kitty, won't you kind me, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.56,0:23:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind is willing, but the body is tired.\NSo we have to say goodbye to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.51,0:23:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We will carry you in our hearts and in our prayers and hope\Nthat we meet again in the hereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, we're going to start the lecture at this time.\NFran will read the slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctors, eyesight.\NIsn't very good anymore, and so he can no longer read the slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.66,0:23:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've asked someone to read the slides for us.\NAnd, uh, we are going to go continue with the lecture and, um, bless you all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.09,0:24:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,for coming such a long way to see us.\NTake that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.81,0:24:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't take snuff.\NOur love for you is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.75,0:24:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being here.\NI'm in the next honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.54,0:24:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to start the lecture.\NThe map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.00,0:25:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A logarithmic.\NScale from one to 1000 where courage is the critical factor point of integrity at 200 below which all the energies are negative and above which all the energies are positive love calibrates 500 and over unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.92,0:25:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates.\NCalibrates at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.66,0:25:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Next slide, please.\NOh, there's slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.30,0:25:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Distribution of the levels of consciousness shown in a pyramid showing that 85% of the world's population calibrates below the level of integrity at 200 and at the top of the pyramid, 15% calibrate above 200, which is the level of courage.\NAn integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.57,0:26:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Distribution of the levels of consciousness shown.\NAnd a fulcrum where the 15% of the world's population that calibrate in integrity over level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.64,0:26:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Counterbalance the 85% of the world's population that calibrate negatively or below level 200 of courage and integrity.\NAnd then 20% of the world's population that calibrate negatively or below level 200 of courage and integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.24,0:26:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Exaggerated.\NAnd we have the animal kingdom. I'll mention some of Doc's favorites. Bacteria 1. Octopus 20. The Komodo dragon at 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.32,0:27:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And at level 200 in the animal kingdom, we reach the grazers, those who do not kill as a means to survive. So the zebra, the gazelle, the giraffe, the deer, the elk, and the family dog at 250.\NAnd we have certain exceptions, such as the kitty's purr at the level of love, 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.33,0:27:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And the doggie's wagging tail at 500. The level of love.\NAnd we see from this next chart that as consciousness level moves up and rises in the map of consciousness, rate of unemployment decreases, rate of poverty decreases, happiness increases, and rate of criminality decreases.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.89,0:28:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So for example, at the level of 50, which is apathy and below.\N97% of people are unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.25,0:28:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,65% are in poverty.\N0% are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.25,0:28:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And 98% criminality.\NHowever, by level 200, which is the critical point of integrity, where the valence of the energy shifts to positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.92,0:28:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only 8% unemployment.\N1.5% poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.92,0:28:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,40% happiness.\NAnd 9.0% criminality.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.14,0:28:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,At the level of love, 5 to 600.\NUnemployment is 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.29,0:28:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Poverty 0.\NHappiness, 98%.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.54,0:29:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Correlation of the levels of consciousness and the rate of happiness.\NAt consciousness level shame, at the bottom of the map of consciousness, only 1% of people are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.54,0:29:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,By the level courage, 255% of people are happy.\NAt the level acceptance, which is logarithm 350, 71% of people are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.77,0:29:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,At level 500, 89% are happy.\NAnd by the time of joy, which is 540 to 599, 99% of people are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.13,0:29:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,99% of people are happy.\NAnd here we have one of the doctor's favorite slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.94,0:30:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The wolf in sheep's clothing.\NThings are not always as they appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.71,0:30:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrations of the great avatars and spiritual teachers.\NJesus Christ, 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.64,0:30:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddha, 1,000.\NZoroaster, 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.53,0:30:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The 12 Christian apostles, 980.\NThe name of God as Om, 975.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.73,0:30:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,John the Baptist, 930.\NMoses, 910.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.21,0:30:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Abraham, 850.\NSt. Paul, 740.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.55,0:31:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual teachers in the 500s.\NThe energy field of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.26,0:31:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,These are historical examples.\NBrother Lawrence, 575.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.33,0:31:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Father Pio, 585.\NConfucius, 590.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.04,0:31:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumi, 550.\NJesus, 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.25,0:31:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dilgo Khyentse Rinpoche, 575.\NSwami Prabhavananda, 550.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.31,0:31:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Love.\NLove is the ultimate law of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.81,0:31:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This statement calibrates 750.\NLove God with all thy heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.16,0:32:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,all thy soul,\Nand all thy mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.16,0:32:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Love thy neighbor as thyself.\NLove makes the world go round.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.85,0:32:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is a many-splendored thing.\NLove is a way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.85,0:32:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is a way to God.\NLove facilitates healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.53,0:32:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the famous duck story.\NI wanted to ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.92,0:32:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say,\NLove God with all your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.92,0:32:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and all your soul,\Nwhat does that mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.91,0:32:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean to you?\NWhat does that mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.91,0:32:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Love God with all your heart\Nand all your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.91,0:32:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and all your mind.\NHow do we apply that to everyday living?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.46,0:32:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You become that love.\NAnd then everything happens
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.53,0:32:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,appropriately,\Nautomatically
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.05,0:32:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,due to what you are.\NSo if you approach a group of people
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.22,0:33:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and the love of God\Nis what motivates you,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.67,0:33:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,all the people in the crowd go,\NHow do they go, folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.13,0:33:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!\NThat's telling them, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.39,0:33:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll show the devil where the hell to go.\NLove God with all your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.09,0:33:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and your mind\Nand you will be wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.25,0:33:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to your fellow man.\NAnd love thy neighbor
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.18,0:33:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,as thyself.\NHow would you interpret that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.81,0:33:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to interpret it.\NYou become that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.01,0:33:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As you become loving,\Nit's your way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.01,0:33:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So lovingness to me\Nis a way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.07,0:33:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an emotion.\NIt's a way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.07,0:33:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, how can I be\Nof help to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.71,0:34:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I comfort you?\NHow can I loan you some money when you're broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.71,0:34:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I help you find a job?\NHow can I console you when you've
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.86,0:34:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,suffered a major loss in your family?\NLovingness is a way of being
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.86,0:34:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world.\NAnd that way you light up the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.36,0:34:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is the way\Nto God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.51,0:34:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true.\NHow do we apply that to our everyday life?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.09,0:34:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.\NYou don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.82,0:34:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\NIs it because that's what you become?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.82,0:34:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you become.\NBecause you become loving,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.09,0:34:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you radiate the energy of God\Nwherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.57,0:34:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are a blessing to be in the world\Nand other people are like a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.30,0:35:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?\NAnd love
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.30,0:35:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,facilitates healing.\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.30,0:35:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Love facilitates healing.\NThat is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.44,0:35:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Love facilitates healing.\NThe more loving you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.17,0:35:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to love all my patients.\NI didn't tell them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.69,0:35:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I loved them all.\NAnd I used to have a patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.03,0:35:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,he had a picture of me\Nand he would go home and he'd put my picture
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.03,0:35:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,on the wall and he would say when he feels\Nbad he looked at the picture and feels better.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.03,0:35:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So that gave me the hint\Nthat love heals.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.03,0:35:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And so as a physician\NI loved all my patients
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.61,0:35:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't tell them.\NMight make them nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.46,0:36:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So as a physician\Nthen you sent love
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.46,0:36:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to the patients you were treating.\NI loved all the patients that I treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.46,0:36:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you were such a success\Nas a psychiatrist
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.46,0:36:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because you were sending them love\Nand thinking about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.92,0:36:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the biggest psychiatric practice\Nin the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.92,0:36:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,for 25 years or whatever.\NWe treated a thousand patients
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.07,0:36:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a year. A thousand patients.\NAnd I loved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.26,0:36:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So if physicians\Nwould say a prayer for their patients
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.26,0:36:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to get better then that would help them\Nrecuperate
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.26,0:36:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,most of the time.\NI prayed over all of them but I didn't tell them I was doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.26,0:36:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It might make them nervous.\NWe have up here the duck story.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.94,0:36:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us the duck story?\NAbout the hunter who
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.94,0:36:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer would hunt?\NOh it makes me cry to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.94,0:36:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can tell it or not.\NBut anyway it's a relatively
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.01,0:37:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,well known story now.\NThis guy hunted ducks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.01,0:37:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a duck hunter.\NJust a normal everyday duck hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.80,0:37:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To me it seems like\Nan abomination to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.80,0:37:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He went duck hunting.\NAnd he shot this duck
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.80,0:37:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and\Nthe duck wasn't killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.28,0:37:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it was\Nbadly injured and the duck
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.28,0:37:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,fell to the ground.\NAnd after this duck fell
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.73,0:37:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to the ground it's mate\Nit's female mate
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.73,0:37:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,flew down on top\Nof the injured duck and she put her
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.98,0:38:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,she put her wings over him.\NAfter that he never killed
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.61,0:38:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,another duck. Okay we'll go on.\NWhat happened to the hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.82,0:38:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah his heart\Nchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.63,0:38:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a transformation\Nwithin his own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.76,0:38:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And he gave up hunting\Nas a sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.21,0:39:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But the female duck\Nfell on top of the male
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.07,0:39:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,duck and she\Nshelled her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.80,0:39:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And he never hunted again.\NSo love has a
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.01,0:39:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,transformative power.\NOnce you become loving
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.61,0:39:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,there are certain things\Nyou can never do again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.23,0:39:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can also perform the miraculous\Nwithout labeling
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.67,0:39:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it miraculous.\NYou can do things other people cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.28,0:39:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And people will do things\Nfor you they would not do for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.34,0:39:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So love has a very\Npowerful transformative effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.73,0:40:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best not to tell\Na lot of people that you love them
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.46,0:40:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because they'll get scared.\NThey'll think you have
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.48,0:40:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,designs on them.\NSo loving this is a way
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.44,0:40:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of being. It's a way of being.\NAnd it transforms
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.61,0:40:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,everything around you\Nbecause of the radiation
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.01,0:40:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of that energy.\NPeople that are hateful
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.71,0:40:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in your presence will suddenly\Nbecome willing to forgive others.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.03,0:40:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll say\Nif you go back over that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.03,0:40:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,how would you do that?\NAnd you can see the person
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.13,0:40:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,transform right in front of you.\NAnd they'd say well I wouldn't have been
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.13,0:40:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,too young to know better.\NThey would find an excuse
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.28,0:40:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to defend the person instead of attack them.\NSo we become defenders
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.76,0:40:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of love and life.\NAnd we stop being
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.76,0:41:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,attackers.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.17,0:41:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was glad during World War II\NI didn't have to kill anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.50,0:41:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to maintain this ship.\NI was a bosun's mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.55,0:41:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I brought the ship through\Nall kinds of terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.61,0:41:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,storms.\NThe ship went over 90 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.34,0:41:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was standing on the bulkhead\Nwith one foot
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.34,0:41:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,on the bulkhead and the other\Nat the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.69,0:41:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I stayed at the wheel for 12 hours non-stop\Nbecause everybody else was sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.69,0:41:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody was terribly seasick\Nand laying on the floor throwing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.78,0:41:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I just stayed\Nat the wheel
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.84,0:41:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess 12 or 20\NI don't know how many hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.61,0:41:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a long couple of days.\NSo love empowers us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.48,0:41:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It allows you to steer a ship for\Nclose to a whole day without food
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.51,0:42:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or drink or\Nanything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.73,0:42:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have had water or something\Nbut I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.34,0:42:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So love empowers us.\NForgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.84,0:42:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and love is\Ntransformative.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.65,0:42:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And we also have to forgive ourself\Nfor our trespasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.65,0:42:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgive myself for the errors\NI have made, oh Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.65,0:42:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was less evolved.\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.23,0:42:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Love calibrates\N500 and over
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.42,0:42:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,on the map of consciousness.\NThe heart chakra
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.42,0:42:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates 505.\NBagpipes
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.90,0:42:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,are an example\Nof the energy of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.90,0:42:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's love of pets.\NLove of freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.90,0:43:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Romantic love.\NLoveless
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.32,0:43:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,equals flat.\NLove of purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.73,0:43:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The golden rule.\NDo unto others
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.73,0:43:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,as you would have them\Ndo unto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.73,0:43:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Love of attributes.\NLove increases
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.86,0:43:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,perceived value.\NLove increases
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.86,0:43:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,happiness.\NLove as
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.46,0:43:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,agape,\Nwhich is universal love,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.46,0:43:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates\N570.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.46,0:43:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Love\Nas virtue.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.71,0:43:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as\Nenthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.73,0:43:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I love doing this.\NLove as
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.34,0:43:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiveness.\NLove as
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.63,0:44:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,acceptance.\NOkay, in this last
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.21,0:44:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,slide, you have given\Nseveral examples of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.21,0:44:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, different types of love.\NLike
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.34,0:44:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,enthusiasm,\Nthe forgiveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.34,0:44:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the acceptance.\NSo each one of these is an
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.34,0:44:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,aspect of love, yet\Nin a different form.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.59,0:44:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?\NWhat's the last thing I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.59,0:44:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But in a different form.\NDifferent forms of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.59,0:44:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all different forms of love.\NWell, you can encourage your
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.59,0:44:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,fellow, you know, to make life better\Nfor everybody around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.78,0:44:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's always been my ambition.\NTo make things go better,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.03,0:44:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,or the eggs got fried better,\Nor the duckies got saved,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.09,0:44:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or the kitty got fed this morning.\NBefore we left the house
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.36,0:44:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,this morning,\Nit was very important to make sure the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.36,0:45:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,kitties had enough food.\NSo we had three kitties all lined up,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.51,0:45:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for their breakfast.\NAnd before we left,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.94,0:45:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we had to make sure the doggie\Nhad enough food and happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.98,0:45:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So to share your love with\Neverything around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.98,0:45:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,kitties and doggies,\Nand other people,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.53,0:45:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and even villains.\NA captured villain,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.80,0:45:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it's up to you\Nto make his life tolerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.09,0:45:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, I'm sorry that I have to\Nhold a gun to your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.09,0:45:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's my job.\NDon't make me pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.17,0:45:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NLove as motivator.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.76,0:45:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Love\Nof creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.65,0:46:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Life.\NExistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.01,0:46:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as appreciation.\NLove as
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.75,0:46:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,kindness.\NLove as essence
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.38,0:46:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of relationship.\NLove as group
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.21,0:46:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,energy.\NExample.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.69,0:46:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcoholics Anonymous.\N540.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.69,0:46:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of unconditional\Nlove.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.69,0:46:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I want you to\Nexplain to everyone here
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.13,0:46:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the difference between\Nlove at 500
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.13,0:46:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and unconditional love\Nat 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.57,0:46:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know that it's that easy\Nto differentiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.57,0:46:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,At 540,\Nyou love everybody and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.19,0:46:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And\Neven Adolf Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.82,0:46:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at him as a person\Nwho was taken over
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.96,0:47:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,by negative energies.\NAnd you're willing to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.38,0:47:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,forgive Adolf Hitler\Nwho couldn't help what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.92,0:47:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to him. That he was\Novercome by evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.69,0:47:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of hating evil,\Nyou feel sorry that people have
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.69,0:47:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,become overwhelmed by evil.\NAnd
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.94,0:47:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Adolf did what\Nhe thought he was required
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.94,0:47:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to do by honor\Nand in its
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.48,0:47:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,contextualization at the time.\NYou can love even Adolf Hitler
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.90,0:47:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in unconditional love,\Nyou would be able to forgive him
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.32,0:47:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and accept him.\NYou'd forgive even Hitler, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.34,0:47:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he was captured by certain\Nideals. Captured by
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.34,0:47:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the thinginess of the time.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.34,0:47:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that everybody\Nwho violates the law of love
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.34,0:48:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is really a victim of\Nsome other
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.46,0:48:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,societal belief system\Nor the pressures of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.59,0:48:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,During the World War\NII, I didn't hate the Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.07,0:48:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after\NPearl Harbor, I didn't hate
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.13,0:48:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitler.\NI didn't hate anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.42,0:48:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So\Nyou still had to conduct yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.57,0:48:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but without hate.\NYou did it out of
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.00,0:48:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a sense of duty and\Nloyalty to your fellow man.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.00,0:48:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The people on the ship,\Nthe only way they got through the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.76,0:48:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okinawa Typhoon,\Nturned over something like
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.82,0:48:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,90 ships. 90 ships went down\Nin the Okinawa Typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.05,0:48:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was at the wheel the whole time.\NYeah. I was just thankful
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.73,0:48:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that, Lord, I could\Nsustain
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.73,0:49:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the life. Everybody was seasick.\NThey were all laying on the deck. It was pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.82,0:49:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody laying on the deck throwing up\Nfor days. It was really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.11,0:49:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And so steering the ship was up\Nto me because I was
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.11,0:49:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the only one, apparently, that wasn't\Nseasick.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.11,0:49:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But we hit 90 degrees because\NI can remember I was standing on the bulkhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.98,0:49:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing up straight on the bulkhead.\NSo we were over 90 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.34,0:49:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So we serve our fellow man\Nout of a commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.46,0:49:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and understanding\Nour human nature
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.19,0:49:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,as God would have us\Nunderstand it. We thank Thee,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.63,0:49:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,O Lord, for our life and we dedicate\Nit to Thy service. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.63,0:49:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Laughter.\NLove as admiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.90,0:49:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as respect\Nas in love of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.32,0:50:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,country and countrymen\Nin the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.51,0:50:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as valor.\NLove of shipmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.71,0:50:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonds\Nof unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.57,0:50:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraternal love\Nas in buddies,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.21,0:50:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,classmates,\Nteammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.21,0:50:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as friendship\Nand loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.94,0:50:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is letting\Ngo of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.53,0:50:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerry Jempolski's book.\NLove as affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.46,0:50:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey.\NSweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.48,0:50:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Love as cherishing.\NMaternal love.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.32,0:50:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-sacrificing.\NLovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.73,0:50:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as an existential\Nstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.86,0:50:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This lecture is the\Nresult of love
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.86,0:51:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and the miraculous.\NI was speaking to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.90,0:51:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,some ladies who were up front here\Nbefore the lecture started
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.90,0:51:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and we were talking\Nabout what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.05,0:51:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to be wives and mothers\Nand how important it is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.05,0:51:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to each one of us\Nto hold that spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.05,0:51:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,torch\Nin our family
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.05,0:51:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and how it's up to us\Nto keep that spirituality
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.05,0:51:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,strong\Nas women of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.05,0:51:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,should be.\NSo I just wanted to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.05,0:51:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,pass that along to everybody\Nthat we as women
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.05,0:51:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as wives\Nand mothers
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.05,0:51:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,need to inspire\Nour children and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.13,0:51:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,mates to\Ntake up that torch
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.13,0:51:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and follow God.\NI love you baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.73,0:52:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Every morning\NI give thanks for your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.73,0:52:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Every night\NI thank God for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.07,0:52:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How animals\Naffect your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.23,0:52:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The songbird's song\Ncalibrates at 500
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.23,0:52:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of love.\NThe kitty's purr
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.42,0:52:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 500\Nthe level of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.42,0:52:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The doggy's\Nwagging tail
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.42,0:52:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 500\Nthe level of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.42,0:53:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The family cat\Ncalibrates at 245
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.42,0:53:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the family dog\Ncalibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.61,0:53:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,at 250\Nand having
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.98,0:53:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a dog\Nincreases your lifespan
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.98,0:53:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,by 10 years.\NYou hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.55,0:53:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,10 years.\NIf you own a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.26,0:53:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you will live 10 years\Nlonger.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.38,0:53:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When you think of all the idiotic\Nexercises, crazy diets
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.38,0:53:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,people go through,\Nwhy don't you just buy a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.59,0:53:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and live 10 more years?\NSave yourself all those horrible
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.59,0:53:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,low cholesterol diets and crap.\NYou get to die of cholesterol
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.86,0:53:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,poisoning when you're 90.\NI don't know, I'm over
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.21,0:53:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How old am I now? I forgot.\NDo you know how old I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.38,0:54:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How old am I? 84.\NIs that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.38,0:54:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well without a dog I would have been\Ndead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.38,0:54:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So Kelsey my doggy at home\Nwho I love and adore.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.82,0:54:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kelsey.\NWhere is Kelsey?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.13,0:54:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's on the screen.\NIs she on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.19,0:54:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to the pound\Nand adopted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.19,0:54:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dave went in and\Nall these dogs are jumping around
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.19,0:54:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,pick me, pick me\Nand here she was just sitting in the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.19,0:54:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and he says I want that one.\NAnd Gabe and I looked at each other like
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.65,0:54:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about her.\NShe's not doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.65,0:54:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He goes no I want that dog.\NAnd we came home with her and she has been a joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.94,0:54:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She herds the kitties.\NAll the other dogs jumped around.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.94,0:54:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kelsey just lay in the corner\Nlike this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.09,0:55:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking out like this.\NSo she got me through the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.15,0:55:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Love me, love my dog.\NBut the fact that owning a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.63,0:55:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,adds ten years to your life.\NI mean that's just a major issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.63,0:55:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years is quite a while.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.30,0:55:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NKelsey asked me to bring that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.01,0:55:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said\NI'll bring it up Kelsey.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.21,0:55:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my promise to her.\NCalibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.17,0:55:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in the level of love.\NThe statement
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.15,0:55:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,love is the ultimate law\Nof the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.15,0:55:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates at\N750.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.11,0:55:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sat Chit Ananda\NCalibrates at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.25,0:56:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Agape\Ntaught by Jesus
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.71,0:56:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates\N570.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.61,0:56:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan Boyle's\Nvoice
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.84,0:56:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates at 550.\NUnconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.98,0:56:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates\N540.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.82,0:56:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The movie The Pacific\NCalibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.88,0:56:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,500.\NWisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.82,0:56:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates at 430.\NMother's Day
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.07,0:56:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates\N300.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.53,0:56:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Solar plexus versus\Nlove.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.76,0:56:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is from the heart.\NAttachment and
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.63,0:56:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,ambitious craving\Nare from the solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.73,0:57:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Examples\Nlove of wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.78,0:57:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Love of fame.\NLove of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.78,0:57:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Love of being right.\NLove of glamour.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.78,0:57:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Publicity.\NLove of stardom.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.78,0:57:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Love of public attention.\NWords that describe
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.01,0:57:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of 500.\NLove.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.01,0:57:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Warmth.\NHeartfelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.01,0:57:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Join.\NAppreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.01,0:57:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nurturing.\NSensual.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.01,0:57:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgiving.\NProtective.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.01,0:57:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Benign.\NInclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.01,0:57:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness.\NAlignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.01,0:57:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Affectionate.\NPurity.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.01,0:57:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Humble.\NCordial.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.01,0:58:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving.\NSatisfying.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.01,0:58:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gracious.\NGenerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.01,0:58:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Passion.\NUplifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.01,0:58:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Holistic.\NSweetness.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.53,0:58:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is a progressively\Nunconditional energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.57,0:58:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovingness is a way of being\Nin the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.30,0:58:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is forgiving.\NNurturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.03,0:58:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And supportive.\NLove emanates from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.61,0:58:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That first statement you said\Nis that love is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.61,0:58:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,progressively\Nunconditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.61,0:58:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you love,\Nthe more you can love.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.78,0:58:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one reason to have a dog.\NYou live 10 years longer
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.01,0:58:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because it brings up\Nthe energy of love
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.01,0:59:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and the energy of love heals\Nand prolongs life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.00,0:59:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're thankful for your life.\NYou're thankful to God
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.61,0:59:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,because of your life.\NAnd you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.61,0:59:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank thee, O Lord, for my life\Nand the miracles of this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.92,0:59:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always thank God\Nfor our dog and our kitties.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.92,0:59:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I thank you for the dog\Nand the kitties.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.92,0:59:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because they represent love.\NThe kitties purr, purr, purr, purr, purr, purr.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.98,0:59:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a kitty that climbs on the bed\Nas soon as we're in bed
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.98,0:59:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it starts to go purr, purr, purr, purr, purr, purr.\NSo we surround
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.98,0:59:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,ourselves with love.\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.03,0:59:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always saying lovingness\Nis a way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.03,0:59:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we apply that to our daily lives?\NYou just become,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.09,0:59:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you become that.\NEverything you do and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.09,1:00:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,every movement,\Nthen is energized by the lovingness
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.09,1:00:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,which you own within yourself.\NEverything I say as I talk
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.65,1:00:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to this audience,\NI feel like an energy running out.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.65,1:00:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to share\Nwhat I hold in my heart
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.65,1:00:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,as a knowingness\Nexperientially
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.38,1:00:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I hold it in my heart\Nfor all of them
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.38,1:00:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that they should all be feeling it.\NI pray for the inner experience
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.53,1:00:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of divine love\Nfor everyone here present now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.53,1:00:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, in the name of the Lord,\Nthe Father, and the Son of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.65,1:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And love is forgiving, nurturing,\Nand supportive.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.75,1:00:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, as a woman you know that.\NIn our society we look to the woman
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.26,1:00:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,as the representative\Nof maternal love as the ideal.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.73,1:01:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NIt emanates.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.01,1:01:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NIt emanates from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.01,1:01:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Love emanates from the heart.\NOh my God, is it emanating someplace here?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.01,1:01:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's emanating.\NFolks help!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.01,1:01:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the emanator squad.\NI can't say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.11,1:01:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say it.\NIt emanates.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.11,1:01:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It emanates.\NAlright.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.25,1:01:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.65,1:01:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you asking me?\NNothing, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.71,1:01:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we're feeling up here\Nbetween you and I,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.38,1:01:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that everyone's picking up out there\Nour love for each other
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.86,1:02:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and everyone is seeing and picking up out there\Nthat vibration.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.05,1:02:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I share with everyone present\Nthat which I feel
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.92,1:02:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,within my heart\Nevery night when I go to bed
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.71,1:02:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank God\Nfor Susan's love every night.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.46,1:02:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you oh Lord.\NAnd because of your presence
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.76,1:02:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel God loves me.\NSo I'm surrounded by your love
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.05,1:02:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and the kitty's love\Nand the doggy's love
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.05,1:02:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and the love of all our friends.\NThe telephone rings all day long
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.05,1:02:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with friends.\NSo she's on the phone with friends
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.69,1:02:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,half the day.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.01,1:02:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.\NWhat's next?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.28,1:02:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna take a real quick break here.\NIt'll be about 15-20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.28,1:03:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll be right back.\NI let it go a little longer
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.28,1:03:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're slow in getting started.\NBut we'll take a quick break
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.28,1:03:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll see you back here\Nin about 15-20 minutes.
